      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for your next road trip. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
