    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is original and aligns perfectly. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats remain supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the 'new car' scent is still present. All electronic systems, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive logbook included. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is free of any debris or oxidation. Riding on original alloy wheels without a single mark of curb rash and wrapped in fresh, high-performance tires, this car offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
